  "instructions": [
    "Dice the barramundi into bite‑size pieces.",
    "Whisk together flour, cornstarch, granulated sugar, smoked paprika, salt, and pepper.",
    "Add the water and egg to the dry mix and stir until smooth.",
    "Add the diced fish to the batter, mixing gently to coat.",
    "Heat the vegetable oil in a deep‑fry pan to 170°C.",
    "Drop spoonfuls of the batter into the hot oil, frying until golden and crisp.",
    "Remove fritters with a slotted spoon and drain on paper towels.",
    "Sprinkle with fresh coriander before serving.",
    "Serve hot with a splash of lime juice if desired."
